OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEveryone must rethink water
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fuse - drought chief        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Everyone who uses water must rethink   
OL,6, and make sure they use it wisely, the  
OL,7, chairman of the body that has declared 
OL,8, droughts around England says.          
OL,10,F"We have got to rethink... and that    
OL,11,Fmeans everyone, not just regulators and
OL,12,Fgovernment," said Harvey Bradshaw,     
OL,13,Fchair of the National Drought Group.   
OL,15,FHe is also executive director of the   
OL,16,FEnvironment Agency, which has warned   
OL,17,Fthe drought could last into next year. 
OL,19,FA Met Office warning of extreme heat is
OL,20,Fcontinuing into Sunday.                
